QuestData.Title: Evil from the Seas
QuestData.Description: I do not know what this evil is that is infesting the forest, $n, but I know exactly how to deal with it. So do you, I think.
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill 8 Darkened Horrors or Darkened Terrors.
QuestData.RewardText: You make me proud, $n. You make all of us proud.

Objectives.Objective: Darkened Horrors or Darkened Terrors slain
